name: Me-O Complete Seafood Adult Cat Food
description: Complete and balanced nutrition for cats. Taurine is an amino acid that is essential for the proper functioning of the eyes and to improve the cat's eyesight. Vitamin C boosts the cat's immune system and helps reduce the detrimental effects of stress on your cat's health. Calcium, Phosphorus and Vitamin D help strengthen teeth and bones. This Formula was developed to help prevent the risk of FLUTD (Feline Lower Urinary Tract Disease). Omega 3 and Omega 6 from quality oil in combination with Zinc will help nourish the cat's hair and skin. *Images for illustration purposes only. Product received may vary.
